  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>Maderno's tucked away on Lake Garda's west coast where there's lots of beautiful views and plenty to keep you busy. Chill out on the beach, head off cycling into the nearby hills or hit the walking trails. There's good ferry and bus links too so you can use it as a base to explore the lake too.</p>]]></listingDescription>
